utschen Betrieben Alltag. Dies liegt auch daran, dass Betriebsräte nur in seltenen Fällen den erforderlichen Strafantrag stellen. ", "ext": {"mediaStats": {"r": "Missing", "ttl": -1}}}]}, "source": "<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Twitter Web App</a>", "in_reply_to_status_id": null, "in_reply_to_status_id_str": null, "in_reply_to_user_id": null, "in_reply_to_user_id_str": null, "in_reply_to_screen_name": null, "user_id": 2283287077, "user_id_str": "2283287077", "geo": null, "coordinates": null, "place": null, "contributors": null, "is_quote_status": false, "retweet_count": 4, "favorite_count": 10, "reply_count": 3, "quote_count": 2, "conversation_id": 1332353931054297093, "conversation_id_str": "1332353931054297093", "favorited": false, "retweeted": false, "possibly_sensitive": false, "possibly_sensitive_editable": true, "lang": "de", "supplemental_language": null, "self_thread": {"id": 1332353931054297093, "id_str": "1332353931054297093"}}}